Package info.kgeorgiy.ja.korolev.implementor

Class Implementor

java.lang.Object
info.kgeorgiy.ja.korolev.implementor.Implementor
All Implemented Interfaces:
Impler, JarImpler
public class Implementor extends Object implements JarImpler
This class provides an implementation of the JarImpler interface for generating an implementation of a given class or interface. The implementation is generated as a Java source file, and optionally compiled and packaged as a JAR file.

    • main

      public static void main(String[] args)
      Parses the command line arguments and generates an implementation of the specified class or interface.

      If the first argument is "-jar", the implementation is compiled and packaged as a JAR file. Otherwise, the implementation is generated as a Java source file.

      Parameters:
      args - the command line arguments, which must be of the form "token root" or "-jar token root"
